summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed from Milwaukee Land Company, an Iowa corporation, to certain lands in Section Four (4), Township Twenty-two (22) North, Range Eight (8) East, W. M., in Cedar River Watershed, King County, Washington, and appropriating One Thousand Eight Hundred Forty-seven and Eighty-three Hundredths ($1847.83) Dollars from Cedar River Watershed Condemnation Fund for the payment of said lands.
